![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578252285253-S5VX77YPPY01IKWG3QQV/image-asset.jpeg)

Endgame is finally in our rear view, and has capped off the unprecedented string of fantastic films that is the Marvel Cinematic Universe! With 22 films under its belt, The Don and GT Rebirth decided to take a good look at the MCU as a whole and RANK ALL 22 FILMS from best to not so good. We even do our best to name the TOP 5 villains of the MCU and the 5 worse! Will you agree with our lists? Only one way to find out with this nostalgia filled episode of the Major Issues Podcast!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
